            <div class="sp_main_header">spefz match</div>
            <p>We have created a unique algorithmic rating system based on personality and physical appearance within the online events dating space. Using a calculated member’s average rating (in percentage), our platform is able to auto-match a specific member to a specific event. This auto matching enables members to meet other members of similar calculated ratings, based on physical appearance & personality, at a live dating event.</p>

            <p>We are the only live event-dating platform to have a unique algorithmic rating and matching system as a core to enable compatibility.</p>

            <p>Our Online events Dating Platform has been in development for the past 12months. It offers our members a high increased probability being matched successfully to their potential partners due to a statistical match-calculation process based on personality & physical appearance. Spefz is a selective social events match-dating platform.</p>

            <p>
              <b>What problem are we solving?</b><br/>
              <span>Our research suggests that, while there is a number of specialist dating events based on ethnicity, culture, religion, sex-orientation, age, professionals etc, most of these specialist-dating events do not analyze their matches for their live dating events. They host their live dating events based on grouping people but not based on a match analyses on interest, preferences, personality and appearance. This results in the increased probability of unsuccessful matches between members at live dating events. </span><br/><br/>
              <span>We aim to solve this problem. What sets us apart is that our platform has an inbuilt algorithm rating and matching system for our live dating events. This algorithm automatically calculates the average rating of each member, uses this average rating to auto-match each member to a specific live dating event (where members with similar average rating score will be present). Our Spefz Team then also takes advantage of the available stats on each member and takes the initiative to introduce members with very close rating scores with one another. The introduction and automated process ensures members are able to meet and connect with like-minded singles and therefore increasing the likelihood of successful matches at each event.</span>
            </p>

            <p>
              <ul>
                <li>We create match-dating events by selling tickets online for the events.</li>
                <li>We also have a subscription based social community that allows our members to stay in touch and grow their network.</li>
              </ul>
            </p><br/>

